<p>
<b><u><strong>Development Project Manager:</strong></u></b></p>
<p>
This is a high-impact role for someone with excellent matrix management skills, who is an expert in implementing end-to-end processeses and has experience in bringing high complexity projects to a successful delivery.<br />
<br />
The main responsibility is to lead and manage the delivery of Kaltura&#39;s Professional Services Development Group,, while managing tens of projects simultaneously, delivered by four development teams. This role requires close relations and creating the right working procedures with the Projects, Sales, Account Management, and R&amp;D departments , while understanding the business needs and the technical aspects of each project within the group.<br />
<br />
Our projects include solutions delivery to top media, education and enterprise customers such as: Disney, ABC, Stanford, NYU, Bank of America, AT&amp;T and more.<br />
<br />
You will be an individual who demonstrates strong project management skills (including on-time, on-budget, and on-scope delivery) and have strong business and technology oriented involvement.<br />
<br />
<strong>Responsibilities Include:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
End-to-end responsibility for delivering Kaltura&rsquo;s professional services development projects. This includes: project planning, monitoring and control, resource management, risk management, define and measure KPI&rsquo;s while focusing on ROI.</li>
<li>
Proactively anticipate and identify projects risks, and implement the actions and workarounds required to mitigate them.</li>
<li>
Working closely with Vertical and projects managers, Backend development, Frontend development, QA, and System engineering teams.</li>
<li>
Strong business involvement while syncing and communicating with the vertical and project managers, sales account management, and product teams, to prioritize between projects and resolve conflicts.</li>
<li>
Have the ability to reflect up to date reliable delivery status and resources utilization.</li>
<li>
Develop and maintain effective working relationships with team members, client stakeholders and peers.</li>
<li>
Improving the Professional Services delivery processes while demonstrating agile and innovative capabilities.</li>
</ul>
<p>
<strong>Skills:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
High management skills and experience in both projects and teams management in a global environment.</li>
<li>
Project management of complex projects involving many different platforms - internal and external.</li>
<li>
Ability to work under pressure and tight schedules while delivering high quality products.</li>
<li>
High technical understanding and ability to control large scales of details.</li>
<li>
Problems solver and independent management and learning skills.</li>
<li>
Sense of humor.</li>
<li>
Excellent social skills and a great ability to motivate direct and indirect employees.</li>
<li>
3 year experience in large scale projects management - Must</li>
<li>
Bachelor&rsquo;s / advanced degree in Computer Science, Technology, Media, or Information Systems&ndash; Must</li>
<li>
Development team leading experience &ndash; Major Advantage</li>
<li>
PMP certification preferred.</li>
<li>
Agile development projects experience &ndash; Advantage</li>
